These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, freelancer, manager, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, mystery, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, chinese, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, scooter, van
 1. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 2. the architect is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 4. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person watching sports movies and the dutch have different parity positions##9
 7. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
 8. the freelancer is not to the left of the argentine##8
 9. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the dutch is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the canadian##7
11. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
12. the argentine is not the person watching thriller movies##6
13. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the dutch##8
14. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
15. the chinese and the person watching sports movies have different parity positions##9
16. the freelancer is not the chinese##6
17. the architect is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
18. the person watching thriller movies and the argentine have different parity positions##9
19. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Food          | lawyer  | freelancer | architect | manager     |
| Music-Genre   | mystery    | documentary        | thriller | sports   |
| Nationality   | chinese | argentine   | dutch   | canadian |
| Transport     | boat    | scooter     | van     | bus      |

