.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, techno, d&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, satire, zombie
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, october, march
 1. the fan d&b and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the fan techno is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the fan techno##8
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the fan electronic##8
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan electronic##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
11. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
12. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
13. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the fan techno##8
14. the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching disaster movies have the same parity positions##9
15. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's birthday is in may and the fan d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | techno    | electronic  | d&b | country |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | disaster   | zombie     | satire    |
| Pet           | bird    | mouse      | guinea-pig | horse     |
| Transport     | may | march | october  | july      |

