.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, japanese, russian
City: boston, london, rome, nizza
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, superhero, disaster, crime
 1. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person watching disaster movies is not the person drinking fanta##6
 3. the person traveling to london is between the person watching spy movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
 5. the person traveling to boston and the japanese have different parity positions##9
 6. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the chinese##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the japanese##8
 8. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 9. the japanese is between the person watching crime movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the japanese and the person traveling to nizza##2
11. the japanese is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
12. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the japanese##8
13. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
14. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
15. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
16. the russian is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | fanta     | hot-chocolate | sprite     | mirinda       |
| Nationality   | colombian | russian       | japanese   | chinese       |
| Pet           | nizza       | rome          | london     | boston           |
| Sport         | superhero   | spy      | disaster | crime |

