4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, horse
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 3. the person drinking fanta and the person traveling to marseilles have different parity positions##9
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
 6. the person traveling to boston and the person who's sport is tennis have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person drinking lemonade##7
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
11. the owner of the goldfish is not the person drinking lemonade##6
12. the person traveling to boston and the person who's sport is tennis have the same parity positions##9
13. the person traveling to boston is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
15. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
17. the person who's sport is rowing is not the owner of the cat##6
18. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5

