The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, coach, nurse, pilot
City: liverpool, colone, berlin, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cricket, sailing, snowboarding
 1. the person driving the tram and the nurse have different parity positions##9
 2. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 3. the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is baseball have different parity positions##9
 4. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 5. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 6. the bartender and the person traveling to colone have different parity positions##9
 7. the nurse is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is not the pilot##6
10. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
11. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is cricket##1
12. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
13. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
14. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's sport is baseball##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Food    | bike | skateboard   | taxi | tram     |
