 8. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person playing go##1
10. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5
11. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5

